  "title": "NPV: The cash flow from a project is projected to be...",
  "summary": "Calculate the NPV of a project by discounting expected cash flows at the appropriate discount rate.",
  "prompt": "The cash flow from a project is projected to be $100,000 per year for 5 years. If the discount rate is 12%, what is the NPV of the project?",
