  "correct_option": "B",
  "answer_text": "B",
  "answer_format": "option_letter",
  "solution": "NPV = Σ (Cash Flow / (1 + r)^t) - Initial Investment. Assuming no initial investment, NPV = ($100,000 / 1.12^1) + ($100,000 / 1.12^2) + ($100,000 / 1.12^3) + ($100,000 / 1.12^4) + ($100,000 / 1.12^5) = $300,000."
